<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>سَمِعْتُ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/5618">أَبِي </a>يُحَدِّثُ، عَنِ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/3807">ابْنِ عُمَرَ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/3783">أَبِي بَكْرٍ </a><span class="special">﵃</span> قَالَ: <span class="c2">«ارْقُبُوا مُحَمَّدًا <span class="special">ﷺ</span> فِي أَهْلِ بَيْتِهِ»</span>.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>